querysource.name: Contacts
querysource.sql:
-- Group: report
-- Name: Customer Profile Report - Contacts
-- Notes: MetaSQL statement for contacts portion of CP report.
-- 20140926:rek added querys to display MT contact fields with temp table -- 20150121:rek Changed Assistant SOS to Secondary Contact/SOS (Support on Site)
-- Group: report
-- Name: Customer Profile Report - Contacts
-- Notes: MetaSQL statement for contacts portion of CP report.
-- 20140926:rek added querys to display MT contact fields with temp table
drop table IF EXISTS temppdfConact;
CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE temppdfConact
as
SELECT
CASE charass_value WHEN 'Assistant SOS' THEN 'Secondary Contact/SOS (Support on Site):' ELSE charass_value||':' END AS charass_value,
(cntct.cntct_first_name||' '||cntct.cntct_last_name||' '|| cntct.cntct_phone) AS NamePhone,
cntct.cntct_title,
cntct.cntct_fax,
CASE WHEN char_length(cntct_email)<19 THEN cntct_email
WHEN char_length(cntct_email) > 37 THEN substring(cntct_email from 1 for 18)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 19 for 18)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 37 for char_length(cntct_email))
ELSE substring(cntct_email from 1 for 18)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 19 for char_length(cntct_email))
END
AS email ,
(CASE WHEN char_length(addr.addr_line2) > 0 AND char_length(addr.addr_line3) < 1 THEN addr.addr_line1||', '||addr.addr_line2
WHEN char_length(addr.addr_line2) > 0 AND char_length(addr.addr_line3) > 0 THEN addr.addr_line1||', '||addr.addr_line2||', '||addr.addr_line3
ELSE addr.addr_line1
END
||', '||addr.addr_city||', '|| addr.addr_state||' '||addr.addr_postalcode) AS address,
(CASE WHEN charass_value = 'Assistant SOS' THEN 1
WHEN charass_value = 'Lead Administrator' THEN 2
WHEN charass_value = 'Technology Lead/Director' THEN 4
WHEN charass_value = 'Public Relations Contact' THEN 5
WHEN charass_value = 'Principal' THEN 3
END) AS TypeOrd
FROM custinfo
JOIN custtype ON (cust_custtype_id=custtype_id)
JOIN crmacct ON crmacct_cust_id = custinfo.cust_id
JOIN cntct ON cntct.cntct_crmacct_id = crmacct.crmacct_id
LEFT JOIN addr ON cntct.cntct_addr_id = addr.addr_id
JOIN charass ON charass_target_id=cntct.cntct_id
JOIN char ON charass_char_id = char_id
WHERE cntct_active
AND charass_target_type='CNTCT'
AND char_name = 'CONTACT TYPE'
AND charass_value <> 'SOS'
AND cust_number = <? value("cust_num_param") ?>;
Insert into temppdfConact
SELECT 'Secondary Contact/SOS (Support on Site):','','','','','',1;
Insert into temppdfConact
SELECT 'Lead Administrator:','','','','','',2;
Insert into temppdfConact
SELECT 'Technology Lead/Director:','','','','','',4;
Insert into temppdfConact
SELECT 'Public Relations Contact:','','','','','',5;
Insert into temppdfConact
SELECT 'Principal:','','','','','',3;
Delete from temppdfConact
where charass_value in
(select charass_value from temppdfConact group by charass_value Having count(*) > 1)
and NamePhone = '';
Select * from temppdfConact
ORDER BY 1, 2, 3;

querysource.sql:
-- Group: report -- Name: Customer Profile Report - Billing -- Notes: Query for Customer Profile Report's billing info -- Group: report -- Name: Customer Profile Report - Billing -- Notes: Query for Customer Profile Report's billing info
--20140929:rek updated for prospects --20141006:rek removed extar billing row
SELECT (bill_cntct.cntct_first_name||' '||bill_cntct.cntct_last_name||' '||bill_cntct.cntct_phone) AS bill_NamePhone, bill_cntct.cntct_title, bill_cntct.cntct_fax AS bill_fax, CASE WHEN char_length(cntct_email)<20 THEN cntct_email WHEN char_length(cntct_email) > 40 THEN substring(cntct_email from 1 for 18)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 19 for 18)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 37 for char_length(cntct_email)) ELSE substring(cntct_email from 1 for 18)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 19 for char_length(cntct_email)) END AS bill_email, (CASE WHEN char_length(cntct_email)<21 THEN cntct_email WHEN char_length(cntct_email) > 40 THEN substring(cntct_email from 1 for 20)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 21 for 20)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 41 for char_length(cntct_email)) ELSE substring(cntct_email from 1 for 20)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 21 for char_length(cntct_email)) END) AS email, (CASE WHEN char_length(cntct_email)<21 THEN cntct_email WHEN char_length(cntct_email) > 40 THEN substring(cntct_email from 1 for 20)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 21 for 20)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 41 for char_length(cntct_email)) ELSE substring(cntct_email from 1 for 20)||' '||substring(cntct_email from 21 for char_length(cntct_email)) END) AS email, (CASE WHEN char_length(bill_addr.addr_line2) > 0 AND char_length(bill_addr.addr_line3) < 1 THEN bill_addr.addr_line1||', '||bill_addr.addr_line2 WHEN char_length(bill_addr.addr_line2) > 0 AND char_length(bill_addr.addr_line3) > 0 THEN bill_addr.addr_line1||', '||bill_addr.addr_line2||', '||bill_addr.addr_line3 ELSE bill_addr.addr_line1 END ||', '||bill_addr.addr_city||', '|| bill_addr.addr_state||' '||bill_addr.addr_postalcode) AS bill_address, 1 as counter FROM crmacct --Note: billing contact is the cust_cntct_id LEFT JOIN custinfo ON crmacct_cust_id = custinfo.cust_id LEFT JOIN cntct bill_cntct ON (cust_cntct_id=bill_cntct.cntct_id) LEFT JOIN addr bill_addr ON (bill_cntct.cntct_addr_id=bill_addr.addr_id)
WHERE crmacct_number = <? value("cust_num_param") ?>
